{"tid":1622363,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［賽後檢討］今晚對家劇本［以己之強護己之短］","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:11:03.000Z","uid":10289,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b9195d8d24f989a4f45581ff4372000d2c931a","tid":1622363,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"今晚好多區都冇狗<br />\n<br />\n對家劇本就係<br />\n想show冇狗-&gt;示威者塞路-&gt;示威者先係暴亂源頭<br />\n（我地自己知真相冇用，鬼佬睇嘢好片面）<br />\n<br />\n12點前全散-&gt;反蒙面法有效止暴制亂-&gt;政府贏輿論<br />\n12點前唔散-&gt;大圍捕-&gt;又唔見手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地最重要嘅係手足</span></span><br />\n要齊上齊落<span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能少</span>！！<br />\n<br />\n對家拎咗輿論，唔緊要。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人最強就係大家嘅文宣同埋創意</span></span><br />\n和理非文宣手足幫我地之後贏返就得。<br />\n<br />\n以己之強護己之短。<br />\n人有不為也，而後可以有所為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結：喺現場嘅退！喺屋企嘅整文宣！</span></span>"},{"pid":"195117538ecc66626a88f6cd254345ad46da128b","tid":1622363,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"張床要人張床要人"},{"pid":"1db7d47f3144b12eee6608a87e62e574bc4c04a1","tid":1622363,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"文宣要人文宣要人"},{"pid":"ac3555df6b000f8e9057c495d7b94b9d12911b4b","tid":1622363,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"張床要人張床要人文宣要人文宣要人"},{"pid":"d79f017cc3bb99eb9b12f303172bc2d4aa156841","tid":1622363,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b0e0